<quantity id="1E099B65FF90FFAEFCADB662FCE9F92D" box="[817,895,1649,1673]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.1" pageId="25" pageNumber="176" unit="m" value="2100.0">2100 m</quantity>
d’altitude; espèce terrestre peu fréquente mais localement abondante.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<caption id="8D8E6608FF93FFADFFEDB0C8FD49FEA1" ID-Table-UUID="8D8E6608FF93FFADFFEDB0C8FD49FEA1" httpUri="http://table.plazi.org/id/8D8E6608FF93FFADFFEDB0C8FD49FEA1" pageId="26" pageNumber="177" startId="26.[113,124,219,237]" targetBox="[115,1197,317,897]" targetIsTable="true" targetPageId="26">
